<emphasis id="4FA7E4AB33196497BA34176CC5FBF698" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">H.-C. Hung, C.-W. Chen &amp; M. Fanerii SITW08836</emphasis>
(BSIP, TAIF[501947], TNM); 
<emphasis id="48B6D41E4852DC9CEC9DD4FFFC622381" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Makira</emphasis>
: Materato to Mt. Gasi, 910 m, 1 Jul 2015, 
<emphasis id="C579748EEB2EDB94F7926762B929CC82" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">H.-C. Hung, C.-W. Chen &amp; M. Fanerii SITW06724</emphasis>
(BSIP, TAIF [482700], TNM). 
<emphasis id="6794CB0AC1F07A9F337EAFB680135BA5" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Papua New Guinea. Manus Province</emphasis>
: Los Negros, 17 Nov 1944, 
<emphasis id="64FD51222CFB7A872FE7C0BFB1C2C586" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">W.H. Wagner Jr. 3277bis</emphasis>
(US [1860271]); 
<emphasis id="787B4AEA6EF0E4897C9B52446C90612B" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">New Ireland</emphasis>
: Ambitle Island, 150 m, 7 Nov 2003, 
<emphasis id="7A2D5A222FF0933C76851B0EA791B4CC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">W. Takeuchi 16691</emphasis>
